Meazure Learning (www.meazurelearning.com) is a full-service testing solutions company for academic, professional and lifelong learners. The result of a merger between ProctorU â€“ the world's largest provider of online, artificial-intelligence-augmented exam security and identity management solutions â€“ and Yardstick Assessment Strategies â€“ a leader in psychometrics and computer-based examination administration for professional testing organizations â€“ Meazure Learning serves the higher education market via the ProctorU brand and the professional testing market via the Yardstick brand. As the first end-to-end testing provider to lead with an online delivery model, Meazure Learning is transforming the testing and assessment landscape. 
 
 
